Keller Williams Capital Realty - Woodstock Branch Brokerage

data.description: Welcome to Littleton, Maine! This updated three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bath home features a completely renovated first floor with all living areas conveniently situated on one level, including laundry. The interior boasts luxury vinyl flooring and neutral wall colors, providing a blank canvas for personalization. The kitchen is equipped with leathered finish granite countertops, a spacious 3x8 island, newer appliances, and a large pantry. The open and spacious main living areas make entertaining easy. The master bedroom includes a sizable walk-in closet and a beautiful master bathroom with a double vanity, marble countertops, a 38x60 walk-in shower, and an oversized linen closet. Bedrooms 2 and 3 offer ample space with generous closet storage. The basement provides potential for additional living space, with a walkout to the extensive backyard. The home features a two-car garage under the family room and kitchen for convenient access. Heating sources include a Weil McLain oil boiler, a Harman P68 pellet stove in the basement, and a Daikin heat pump added in November 2022 for air conditioning. Situated on a 10.9-acre parcel just outside Houlton, Maine, with low Littleton taxes, this property is only 11 minutes from Walmart, grocery stores, and shopping. The backyard includes a 14x32 Amish shed with reinforced flooring and a roll-up garage door. Enjoy plenty of outdoor space for activities on the large, level lot, extending to Big Brook for fishing. If you're pre-approved for a mortgage and interested in this home, contact us for a personal showing.
